        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "クジラが水面を突き破る、ダイナミックなブリーチングの瞬間を写真に収めた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "イルカが頻繁にブリーチングを繰り返す様子は、見ているだけで楽しい。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「あのクジラのブリーチング、迫力満点だったね！」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "gloss": "(wall) breaching (to reach trapped people)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "洪水で決壊した堤防（breaching）から、濁流が住宅街へと流れ込んだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "津波の襲来により、海岸沿いの施設が次々とbreaching（破壊）されていった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「敵の防御壁をbreaching（突破）して、一気に城内へ突入しよう！」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
